OL,3,CBritish couple detained in Iran
OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FLindsay and Craig Foreman were
OL,7,Farrested while travelling through Iran
OL,8,Fin January 2025 and later accused of
OL,9,Fespionage ` charges they deny. Both
OL,10,Fare being held in Tehran's notorious
OL,11,FEvin prison, where many foreign
OL,12,Fnationals and political detainees are
OL,13,Fconfined. They told family members
OL,14,Fthey were informed of the sentence
OL,15,Fearlier this week.
