OL,3,CBritish couple detained in Iran
OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FThe development came shortly after
OL,7,FCraig Foreman told ITV News he and his
OL,8,Fwife were being "held hostage" by the
OL,9,FIranian authorities, describing the
OL,10,Freality of their detention during two
OL,11,Ftelephone interviews.
OL,13,FThe sentence is unusually long ` twice
OL,14,Fthe five-year term imposed on Nazanin
OL,15,FZaghari-Ratcliffe, the British-Iranian
OL,16,Fdual national whose detention became
OL,17,Fone of the most high-profile
OL,18,Fdiplomatic disputes between London and
OL,19,FTehran.
