OL,3,CBritish couple detained in Iran
OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FJoe Bennett, Lindsay Foreman's son,
OL,7,Fsaid: "My parents have now been
OL,8,Fsentenced to ten years following a
OL,9,Ftrial that lasted just three hours and
OL,10,Fin which they were not allowed to
OL,11,Fpresent a defence. They have
OL,12,Fconsistently denied the allegations.
OL,13,FWe have seen no evidence to support
OL,14,Fthe charge of espionage.
OL,16,F"We are deeply concerned about their
OL,17,Fwelfare and about the lack of
OL,18,Ftransparency in the judicial process.
