OL,6,FCraig Foreman gave his first interview
OL,7,Ffrom prison hours earlier, describing
OL,8,Fthe message he wanted to send to the
OL,9,FBritish government. "One word would
OL,10,Fbe: 'help'. Full stop," he told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,F"I don't understand why we have been
OL,14,Fhere for 13 months, being held hostage
OL,15,Fin 2026. In what day and age does this
OL,16,F(happen?) When does this end?"
