OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FHe described harsh conditions,
OL,7,Fincluding 57 days in solitary
OL,8,Fconfinement. "I was weeping, crying
OL,9,Fmany nights ` many days," he said,
OL,10,Fspeaking over a crackly prison phone
OL,11,Fline interrupted by automated messages
OL,12,Fin Farsi.
OL,14,F"Emotionally and physically, it broke
OL,15,Fme to pieces."
OL,17,FHe described being held in "an eight-
OL,18,Ffoot cell with a hole in the floor and
OL,19,Fa sink... they are disgusting.
