OL,6,F"You have nothing to read. You have
OL,7,Fnothing to look at."
OL,9,FHe is now held in a larger shared room
OL,10,Fwith other foreign prisoners.
OL,12,F"We are 12 people in this room...
OL,13,Fprobably eight metres by four metres,"
OL,14,Fhe said. "So the room is tight. But
OL,15,Fit's workable. So, it's got a good
OL,16,Fworking relationship in my room."
OL,18,FCraig Foreman also described the
OL,19,Fmoment of his arrest, four days after
OL,20,Farriving in Iran.
