OL,3,CBritish couple detained in Iran
OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FHe said armed plain-clothes officers
OL,7,Fand uniformed personnel seized their
OL,8,Fdevices before returning later to
OL,9,Ftheir hotel.
OL,11,F"They escorted us from the hotel,
OL,12,Fblindfolds on, we're bundled into the
OL,13,Fback of the car, told not to talk, and
OL,14,Fescorted to a police station."
OL,16,FThe Foremans had been asked to return
OL,17,Fto their accommodation so police
OL,18,Fofficers could search their devices.
OL,19,F"I guess maybe four hours later, it
OL,20,Fwas late, maybe five hours."
