OL,6,F"And, I could say half a dozen plain
OL,7,Fclothes police all in black came into
OL,8,Fthe hotel, all with their helmets on,
OL,9,Ftheir phones filming us."
OL,11,FLast week, ITV News spoke to Lindsay
OL,12,FForeman, who is being held in a
OL,13,Fseparate wing of the same prison. She
OL,14,Fdescribed what she called
OL,15,Fpsychological torture ` being promised
OL,16,Frelease, being told she would see her
OL,17,Fhusband, and then discovering those
OL,18,Fpromises were false.
