OL,4,C'sentenced to ten years', family say
OL,6,FCraig Foreman said the rare meetings
OL,7,Fbetween them are essential. "I know
OL,8,Fher prison is just 70 metres away, and
OL,9,FI get to see her once a month," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"For me and for Lindsay, seeing each
OL,13,Fother is the only thing that's keeping
OL,14,Fus going right now. I love my wife
OL,15,Fdearly. She's the love of my life."
OL,17,FThe couple expect to appear before a
OL,18,Fcourt in Tehran in the coming days.
